{Here [/variation/37827290/#/24/w] we see examples of how, in total chaotic situations, knowing the Cemento Spirit can help us navigate through all the turbulences!} 1. b4 $3 {It is so important to know that activating the bishop starting with b3-b4 pawn push can give us the necessary stability in these crazy Breyer (Spassky`s brilliant piece sac) positions! Once we establish the cemented bishop on b3, the time will come to start looking at the opponent's king!} *

