tion we have reached back to the famous Polgar-Spassky game.} cxd5 20. cxd5 Nbxd5 21. exd5 Nxd5 22. Rac1 $3 {The advantage of the engines is that they hardly get shocked and they simply try to find the best moves under any condition... We'll see fascinating lines in my survey [/variation/37827290/#/1/w] on 18. Be3.} *

