18... Re8 {White can get a decisive advantage with simple, practical chess. How?} 19. Bg5 $1 h6 (19... Bf8 20. Nh5 $1) 20. Nxe7+ {I decided to be practical. Knowing that I had an enormous advantage, I felt there was no need for fancy tactics.} (20. Bxh6 $5 gxh6 21. Nxh6+ Kf8 22. Bb3 $3 {Honestly, I had missed this stunning computer move during the game.}) 20... Qxe7 21. Nf5 Qe6 22. Bxf6 Qxf6 23. Nxd6 Red8 24. e5 {Winning a healthy pawn and cementing the knight on d6 was too tempting.} Qg5 25. g3 {And I went on to win the game without much effort.} *

