23. Qb1 $1 {Final question for you: should Black trade queens or keep them?} Qc7 $1 {Black must absolutely keep the queens on the board.} (23... Qxb1 $6 {Clearly, I was hoping for the queen trade when Black faces a rather unpleasant defensive task.} 24. Rxb1 $14 {White can activate the rook on the b-file and putting pressure on the d6-pawn is easier.}) 24. Qb2 Ng6 25. Ra1 {White can't tolerate the black rook on the open file.} Rxa1+ 26. Qxa1 {With approximate equality. That's all for now!} *

