20... Bg7 {How should White continue?} 21. b3 Ncb6 22. Ng4 $1 {This move (maneuver) is the reason why Black usually places his knight on e5...} Ne5 23. Ne3 $1 {Back in 2015, this was my favorite route, and I was very happy when I discovered it...} (23. Nh6+ {is now an empty shot.} Kh8 {There is no follow-up.}) 23... Bc8 $6 24. f4 Ned7 25. Nef5 $3 {Another brilliant idea I discovered while checking this line.} gxf5 26. Nxf5 $16 {With long-term attack. Again, the Nf5 sacrifice!} *

