16... Bg7 {I already had something very special in mind! What could that be?} 17. Nh6+ $1 {Yes, this is it! We see some very special motifs here.} Kf8 {Whenever Black has to make an ugly move like this against the Nh6 check (the same applies to ...Nh3 check vs. White's king), then one needs to look out for special ideas...! How do we continue the initiative?} 18. b3 $1 {Yes, first, we ensure that Black is completely paralyzed on the queenside! We can take this luxury because Black has no good moves. Besides, we are also preparing some devilish threats.} Nb7 (18... c6 19. Qd2 $1) 19. h4 $1 {Typical.} c6 {Now comes the real point, which I had been playing for! What is the devilish move?} 20. Qd2 $3 {This a very special move that completely destroys Black.} cxd5 (20... f6 {Fressinet played this, but it is a strategic capitulation... We'll see next how to proceed.}) 21. Ng5 $1 {The killer!} Bxh6 22. Nxh7+ {With a winning attack.} *

