34... Kf8 {What happens here? Pay attention to Black's resources!} 35. Nxd6 $1 Bxf2+ $3 {This disturbed me. What is the move here?} (35... Rxa1+ 36. Kh2 Qa7 {leads to mate:} 37. Qxf6 Be8 38. Ng6+ Kg8 39. Qh8#) 36. Kh2 $1 (36. Kxf2 $2 Qb6+ {is winning for Black!}) 36... Bxh4 37. Nxb7 Rxa1 38. Nc5 {With a clear advantage, but I was not so sure about this unbalance of rook + two pieces vs. queen situation. According to engines, this is just completely winning due to the missing coordination of Black's forces...} *

