35... Qc7 {I missed a simple win here. Can you find it?} 36. Bg5 $1 {This was much stronger than the game.} (36. Bd2 Rxf1+ 37. Kxf1 g6 $1 {This cuts White's coordination. White's still winning here, but I erred again in time trouble.}) 36... Rxf1+ 37. Bxf1 Nh7 38. Bh4 $1 Nef6 39. Nh6 $1 {This idea also existed in the game, but here it is stronger thanks to the bishop.} Be8 40. Nc6 $1 {Again, a picturesque position! Black is completely paralyzed.} *

